title: 09/29/21 DPS Hour 2 Brian Kelly
itunes:title: 09/29/21 DPS Hour 2 Brian Kelly
description:
Brian Kelly tells Dan that he celebrated the win over Wisconsin by riding in bumper to bumper traffic in Chicago. Coach Kelly says having Chicago style pizza on the bus took him back to his early days of coaching.
